From the manufacturer

Meet The Polaroid Zip

Polaroid Zip App

Previous page

  1. Expert Editing

    The Polaroid Zip app provides more than the standard crop and rotate options. Get the picture-perfect print by adjusting brightness, color temperatures, blur settings, and more.

  2. Creative Collages

    Print up to four images on a single photo with the apps collage mode. Momentous photo montages are just a moment away.

  3. Fantastic Filters + Frames

    Set the mood with the apps wide array of unique filters. Then add a fun frame to finish off your photo.

  4. So Many Stickers

    Add some goofy fun to your Polaroid prints by adding themed stickers directly from the Polaroid Zip app.

  5. Dazzling Doodles

    Use your phones touchscreen to draw directly on your photos. From pictures to messages to smiley faces, the possibilities are only limited by your own creativity.

Next page

Instant Printing Perfection

Previous page

  1. On-the-Go Printing

    Pack the Polaroid Zip in your pocket and youre ready to print anytime, anywhere.

  2. Print from your Phone

    The Polaroid Zip connects wirelessly with Bluetooth, so theres no computers needed.

  3. Print and Post

    Polaroid Zip photos are sticky-backed, so you can post them on notebooks, laptops, and more.

  4. Plenty of Prints

    The powerful built-in battery supports up to 25 prints on a single charge.

Next page
1 Portable Printing 2 Bluetooth Connectivity 3 Sticky-Backed Photos 4 Rechargeable Battery

ZINK Zero Ink Technology

Previous page

  1. Green-Friendly Photos

    No cumbersome cartridges required. By removing the need for ink and toner, ZINK paper cuts down on the waste that goes into landfills, resulting in a happier, healthier planet.

  2. Lifeproof Prints

    Every shot from your Polaroid Zip printer is made to last a lifetime. Each 2x3 sheet is treated with a protective layer that shields it from tears, water damage, and smudges.

  3. Made in the USA

    The ZINK development and manufacturing facility is located in Whitsett, North Carolina. Thats where each sheet of ZINK paper is carefully created by American hands.

  4. Inkless Printing

    No need for ink, toner, or cartridges: ZINK paper is all you need. Thats because each sheet is embedded with color crystals that automatically activate every time you take a picture.

  5. Highly Detailed Prints

    Enjoy vibrant full-color instant photos with a level of detail only possible through ZINK ZERO INK Technology.

Next page

Simple Setup For Fast Photos

Previous page

  1. Step One

    Open paper tray. Insert Polaroid ZINK Paper. Ensure blue calibration sheet is at the bottom.

  2. Step Two

    Press and hold power button. The light will turn on, indicating the device is on.

  3. Download App

    Download Polaroid Zip App from Google Play Store or Apple App Store.

  4. Step Four

    Use the app to personalize photos. Then tap the print button to watch your photos come to life!

Next page
1 Load Paper 2 Power On 3 Download App 4 Edit + Print

What makes the Polaroid Zip unique?

The Polaroid Zip makes it possible to print any picture on your phone or social media account. Add a mountain of editing features, and this portable printer becomes a handheld print studio.

Does the Polaroid Zip come with ZINK paper?

The Polaroid Zip comes with a starter pack of ZINK paper, so you can start printing pictures right away.

Is the Polaroid Zip App required in order to use this printer?

Yes. The Polaroid Zip app must be installed on an Apple or Android device in order to edit and print photos.

Can I print photos that are on my social media page?

Yes. The Polaroid Zip app allows you to access photos from social media, so you can then edit, save, and print them.

Do I need to replace the batteries?

This printer comes equipped with a rechargeable battery, so theres no need to replace it. The Polaroid Zip can print up 25 photos before it needs to be recharged with the included charging cable.

Print your social media and camera memories instantly with the unique Polaroid ZIP Mobile Printer. Simple one-touch operation makes it easier than ever for the whole family, from kids to young adults, to get in on the instant print action! Just connect to your smart phone or tablet via Bluetooth or NFC, and watch your pictures come to life as pocket-sized photo prints that you can share.

5.0 out of 5 starsEdit on your phone, not within the app.
September 23, 2016
Color: WhiteStyle: Printer Only
I was iffy about buying this after reading all the reviews saying the images printed dark. The trick is to make the image lighter on your phone, do not edit within the app. The picture on the left was made brighter within the app and the one on the right was edited on my phone first. Love this product.

Camille Perezselsky
5.0 out of 5 starsFun printer, Make sure you download the updated App!
November 26, 2017
Color: BlackStyle: Printer OnlyVerified Purchase
This is a really fun little printer! The print quality is good and suited for the purpose of instant photo gratification. If you are expecting studio quality prints than this probably isnt for you. But, if youre looking for an instant camera to print photos at parties, for crafts, and to get your pics out of the digital space then give this printer a try. You can edit photos to your hearts content in the app prior, and because you are using your phone camera the picture quality/zoom/colors come out nicer than with a point and shoot instant camera. The paper is more economical than other instant camera options, around $22 for a 50 pack of paper.

Some advice.
Make sure you scan the QR code on the back of the box and download the correct app, Polaroid Zip NOT the QR code from the instruction booklet- it is outdated and the app doesnt work. The Correct app is called Polaroid Zip its black with a rainbow icon for iPhones. There are two versions in the Google Play App Store, if you download the wrong one you wont be able to print!

Overall we are really happy with our purchase.
